pokepower.text:
Once during your turn (before your attack), you may move a {R}
					Energy attached to 1 of your Pokemon to Heatran. This power can't
					be used if Heatran is affected by a Special Condition.

Once during your turn (before your attack), you may move a {M}
					Energy attached to 1 of your Pokemon to Heatran. This power can't
					be used if Heatran is affected by a Special Condition.
